<LG N="64">
<PB N="17" REF="001030_0028_0FAEEEDEDC06E958">
<HEAD>(64)</HEAD>
<L>Why,<NOTE PLACE="marg"><HI>Luk.</HI> 13.34. J<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">h 5.40 <HI>&amp;</HI> 15 22</NOTE> when he &s;tood <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ff'ring his Blood</L>
