</LG>
<LG N="73">
<HEAD>(73)</HEAD>
<L>His Ma&s;ters will how to fulfill</L>
<L>the &s;ervant that well knew,</L>
<L>Yet left undone his duty known,<NOTE PLACE="marg"><HI>Luk.</HI> 12.47. <HI>Mat.</HI> 11.21, 2<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> 24.</NOTE></L>
<L>more plagues to him are due.</L>
