<HEAD>(76)</HEAD>
<L><NOTE PLACE="marg"><HI>Is An+&s;wered. Luk</HI> 13 27 <HI>Mat</HI> 22.12.</NOTE>To whom the Lord t<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">us in a word</L>
