<L><NOTE PLACE="marg"><HI>Mat.</HI> 6.21, 24 <HI>R<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">m.</HI> 1.25</NOTE>your hearts led on &s;ome Lu&s;t:</L>
